{"about_the_game":"Welcome back!<br><br>The game nobody expected is getting a sequel no one's ready for - bigger and more chaotic than the last.<br><br>If you have not played the first game - feel free to start here. Lingo 2 has a totally new rule structure, so you can play them in either order.<br><br>If you did play the first game and <i>only</i> enjoyed solving the word puzzles - you might want to let a friend try this first. There's always Scrabble!<br><br>Featuring...<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>New Puzzle Mechanics</strong> - A complete overhaul to the system you had finally figured out. Beginner friendly!<br></li><li><strong>Wandering</strong> - A large, winding, interconnected world to get lost in.<br></li><li><strong>Music</strong> - Soundtrack by Icely!<br></li><li><strong>Jumping</strong> - You can jump! It's not useful, but who doesn't love to jump?<br></li><li><strong>Minimal Linearity</strong> - An open world that unfolds as you explore it.<br></li><li><strong>Ominous Questions</strong> - Nothing scary; just making sure you remembered to switch the laundry.<br></li><li><strong>Cubes</strong> - I didn't count or anything, but there are a few more cubes this time.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523310/extras/WHEREGIF.gif?t=1735775033\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523310/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735775033","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523310/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735775033","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523310/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735775033","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523310/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735775033","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3375440,"descri